  "details": "SciPy (pronounced \"Sigh Pie\") is open-source software for mathematics, science, and engineering. It includes modules for statistics, optimization, integration, linear algebra, Fourier transforms, signal and image processing, ODE solvers, and more.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nA refcounting issue which leads to potential memory leak was discovered in scipy commit 8627df31ab in Py_FindObjects() function.(CVE-2023-25399)",
